This week we secured $200 million for Everglades Restoration, which funds critical projects like the Southern Storage Reservoir. Check it out: https://youtu.be/MlkFJ6joj4M

Christmas came early for the Everglades! → Congress has nearly tripled funding for critical projects like the EAA Southern Storage Reservoir to store and treat water south of Lake Okeechobee. This is a huge victory in our fight to stop harmful discharges! https://www.tcpalm.com/story/opinion/editorials/2019/12/20/federal-government-donald-trump-sends-christmas-present-south-florida-environment-thumb-up/2685655001/ …

It’s unacceptable for the Department of Veterans Affairs to use taxpayer dollars to fund cruel, unnecessary experiments on animals at the VA.
